download.location: maven central, apache dist, apache nexus

ossc.notes: Apache Felix Gogo is an apache release and thus needs no further approval. The org.apache.felix.gogo.command-0.16.0-sources.jar is not included in the release. It was built by David Jencks locally from the released org.apache.felix.gogo.command-0.16.0-project.tar.gz by changing the maven-bundle-plugin to 1.4.3 in the pom.xml and running mvn source:jar.
